		"_comment": [
			"These describe the various kinds of buttons found on controllers in the database.",
			"shape is the shape of the button itself",
			"icon (may be absent) is the symbolic name of the button's legend",
			"text is a best-effort Unicode representation of the legend",
			"text_basic (may be absent if text is all ASCII) is a best effort ASCII representation of the legend",
			"shape_is_button is defined and true if the shape is itself the button, and an additional icon or text would be redundant.",
			"The idea is a new button of an old shape can be drawn by games using the database even without explicit support by invoking a text renderer with Unicode support."
		],

